               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-44va)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6rb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 6va-8va)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fols. 8va-9va)&#xD; I-4) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 47 miracles (fols. 9va-44va), incomplete&#xD; II)
                     Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus" (fols. 45ra-66vb)&#xD; II-1) ʾƎsaggǝd
                     la-malakotǝka ... "I worship Thy Godhead ..." (fols. 45ra-47rb)&#xD; II-2)
                     Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus": 12 miracles (fols. 47rb-66vb)&#xD; III)
                     Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel Miracles of Michael": 2 miracles (fols. 66vb-68ra)&#xD; IV)
                     Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 1 miracle (fol.
                     68ra-vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
